OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,FA mum has told a court her family will
OL,7,Fbe "forever heartbroken" after her
OL,8,Fdaughter was stabbed to death by her
OL,9,Fboyfriend.
OL,11,FMichael Ormandy, 34, was jailed for
OL,12,Flife with a minimum of 24 years after
OL,13,Fhe stabbed his girlfriend Rebekah
OL,14,FCampbell 27 times inside her flat in
OL,15,FApril 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
