OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,FA statement from Rebekah's mum,
OL,7,FDeborah Woolerton, was read to
OL,8,FLiverpool Crown Court during a hearing
OL,9,Fon Thursday 16 October.
OL,11,FShe said: "Rebekah, our beautiful
OL,12,Fdaughter. We should not have to be
OL,13,Fhere today wishing she was still with
OL,14,Fus, having fun, living life to the
OL,15,Ffull, making others smile, making
OL,16,Fplans for the bright future she had
OL,17,Fahead of her. Our hearts are broken,
OL,18,Fand we will never ever be the same
OL,19,Fwithout her in our lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
