OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"Rebekah had her whole life ahead of
OL,7,Fher and shouldn't have been taken away
OL,8,Fso young. All she wanted in life was
OL,9,Fto be happy and one day have a little
OL,10,Ffamily of her own. Most of all, she
OL,11,Fwanted children. We won't get to see
OL,12,Fher do any of these things now.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
