OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"Rebekah was kind, loving, and she
OL,7,Floved her life. She loved making new
OL,8,Ffriends and looking after everyone,
OL,9,Fmaking sure everyone was ok. That made
OL,10,Fher happy. She was always learning new
OL,11,Fbeauty treatments so she could treat
OL,12,Fher friends and family and make them
OL,13,Fall look and feel beautiful, inside
OL,14,Fand out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
