OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"Rebekah was not just my daughter, she
OL,7,Fwas my best friend, always there to
OL,8,Fcheck I was alright. I would see her
OL,9,Fnearly every day, sometimes a couple
OL,10,Fof times a day. If she couldn't come
OL,11,Ffor some reason, she would ring,
OL,12,FFaceTime or text.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
