OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"Rebekah was the best big sister to
OL,7,FJaime. She spoiled and looked after
OL,8,Fhim. They were so close. They went
OL,9,Feverywhere together, even on nights
OL,10,Fout and walks with her dog Clio, who
OL,11,Fwas her baby. He isn't coping with the
OL,12,Fheartache. We are so heartbroken.
OL,13,FRebekah has left a great big hole in
OL,14,Four family. Life is never going to be
OL,15,Fthe same.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
