OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"On the 16th of April, Rebekah was
OL,7,Fkilled in the most horrific
OL,8,Fcircumstances. It tortures me so much
OL,9,Fto think of how she suffered at the
OL,10,Fhands of Mick Ormandy, who she had
OL,11,Fonly met about 10 or 12 weeks earlier.
OL,12,FShe must have been so scared. I
OL,13,Fstruggle to sleep, and if I do sleep I
OL,14,Fhave terrible nightmares all the time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
