OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"I think of this every day. It causes
OL,7,Fme to shake, inside and out, feel sick
OL,8,Fand cry all the time. I now have to
OL,9,Ftake antidepressants and beta blockers
OL,10,Fto try to stop the shaking and just to
OL,11,Ftry and help me get through the day.
OL,12,FDoctors said it's PTSD. That could be
OL,13,Fwith me all the time now. This should
OL,14,Fnever have happened to Rebekah, just
OL,15,Fbecause she didn't want to be in a
OL,16,Frelationship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
