OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"No parent, brother, family or friend
OL,7,Fshould ever have to go through this.
OL,8,FWe couldn't give Rebekah a big hug,
OL,9,Ftell her we loved her or say goodbye,
OL,10,Fbecause he took her from us in this
OL,11,Fhorrible and traumatic way.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
