OL,3,CFamily 'forever heartbroken' as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murder of Rebekah Campbell
OL,6,F"I will never understand how or why he
OL,7,Fdecided to do this to our lovely
OL,8,FRebekah, who was just so nice to
OL,9,Feveryone. We are and will be forever
OL,10,Fheartbroken. Rebekah won't be
OL,11,Fforgotten. My beautiful baby girl. We
OL,12,Fmiss her so much every day. It's so
OL,13,Fwrong that we are made to go through
OL,14,Fthis pain. Shine bright Rebekah and
OL,15,Fwatch over us all, especially Jaime.
OL,16,FWe will miss you and your great big
OL,17,Fsmile always."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
